#. type: itemize
#: documentation_developer.tex:31
msgid ""
"\\directory{tmp/} A directory for temporary files. There is no automatic "
"cleanup yet."
msgstr ""
"\\directory{tmp/} Ein Verzeichnis für temporäre Dateien. Es gibt noch keine "
"automatische Bereinigung."

#. type: itemize
#: documentation_developer.tex:31
msgid ""
"\\directory{upload/} The destination for uploaded content. Currently only "
"specific *.PEP files produced by Awinta ASYS Smart are understood. Those "
"files contain information about the amount of customers that have been "
"served in the past."
